CODE TO INSTALL  ABACUS MILTARY HELICOPTERS NOTE: IT IS IN THE ZIP FILES AS WELL 



MHE-XDAPYD-AHMBQD-PHKBSV
280 kb, that's gonna be one huge heli ;-)

I grew curious about the serial and downloaded the *other* Abacus Military Helicopters -package available on this site.
It turned out that the serial that redarrows offers is working perfectly with the other package - I will try to put together a nice reseed of both the Abacus Military Helicopters and the correct serial later today.
